{"tid":2266194,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 再度回擊惡意網民提告　「已提出告發、告訴，也會採取民事相關措施」","createTime":"2020-11-01T06:07:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T08:14:03.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b1bb1d367c27ad618e01ac75ec8bfff8973327f7","tid":2266194,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:07:49.000Z","msg":"隨著 TWICE 回歸，粉絲的迴響和 anti 的惡意言論同時湧現，JYP 最近也重申以法律手段保護 TWICE 的立場！<br />\n<br />\nJYP Entertainment 昨天（10 月 31 日）在 TWICE 的官方網站上發布了一篇公告，指出最近有人以特定社群為中心發布、散佈謠言，目前已經針對這些貼文提出告發或告訴，而且還會視惡意行為的特性與嚴重性所造成的直 / 間接傷害規模，在近日採取民事相關措施。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_ef35a5084f2a79c2d791dbb86077a6b3/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-01/131325-882856.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_ef35a5084f2a79c2d791dbb86077a6b3%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-01%2F131325-882856.png&h=758bb387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJYP 並表示：「正如我們已數度發出的聲明，無論是撰寫、隨意發布或散佈這類言論，全都是我們採取法律手段處置的對象，還請各位留意，不要因此招致不必要的傷害。」<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，TWICE 在本週發行第三張正規專輯〈Eyes wide open〉後立刻展開了打歌活動，今天也公開了特別拍攝的舞蹈影片！<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"0887544f38102bf3496ebfbf00babb7d7aa9e1ab","tid":2266194,"uid":256796,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:08:57.000Z","msg":"我已提出告發印家軍首領嘅民事訴訟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e33a43c870142198c2bc0dfa3ec063ac1e5d9833","tid":2266194,"uid":284432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:09:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7e6c2beae6f3194cdd77304639dab1717844f9c3","tid":2266194,"uid":320204,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T06:10:19.000Z","msg":"導狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9129ab7ac8f0ab2476f6a8dd40fd40ee85bcd39b","tid":2